<span class="line"><span style="--shiki-light:#D73A49;--shiki-dark:#F97583;">JIRA_BASE_URL</span><span style="--shiki-light:#24292E;--shiki-dark:#E1E4E8;">=https://your-domain.atlassian.net</span></span>
